// Hot Reload — the Essentials second album. Warm electronica in daylight:
// detuned electric pianos, brushed and micro-programmed rhythm machines,
// melodies computed once and returned from memory. Where First Light was
// the night drive, this is the afternoon build — nested blocks all the
// way down, every lane a family of variants.
// Listen: forte play packages/essentials_0.6.0/albums/hot-reload
block HotReload {
  desc "Warm daylight electronica: detuned keys, brushed micro-grooves and melodies served from memory — nested blocks all the way down. The afternoon build to First Light's night drive."
  tags "album, electronica, downtempo, warm, ambient, idm"
  artist "Forte Essentials"
